{"tid":118086,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死6隻]客貨車撼運木車釀6死3傷　起火燒剩支架","createTime":"2017-02-12T17:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T17:32:47.000Z","uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7f1a0362e415970ea3ecbc6cb0fc93df72c0d58","tid":118086,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:30:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170212/bkncn-20170212135022108-0212_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170212%2Fbkncn-20170212135022108-0212_05011_001.html&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbZnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=27a0c4db\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170212/bkncn-20170212135022108-0212_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170212/photo/bkncn-20170212135022108-0212_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170212%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170212135022108-0212_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=e68ee65c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東梅河高速公路（梅州至河源）雞雄山隧道口今日凌晨發生奪命車禍，一輛客貨車與一輛運木貨車相撞，造成客貨車上6人死亡、3人受傷，傷者經送院治療後已無大礙。該路段的清理工作已於清晨6時40分完成，道路目前亦已恢復通行。<br />\n<br />\n事發於今日凌晨2時44分左右，客貨車沿梅河高速公路往興寧市方向行駛時，在雞雄山隧道口與一輛裝載木材的貨車相撞後起火。消防接報到場救援，並拖喉向客貨車射水灌救。從現場圖片可見，客貨車被燒剩支架，冒出濃濃白煙。<br />\n<br />\n大火被救熄後，消防在客貨車上發現6具屍體，並將其餘3名傷者送院搶救。警方經初步調查，證實客貨車為東莞籍，而大貨車則為福建籍。目前事故的調查及善後工作仍在進行中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4a1e78b18a4ba868db552cad40f2c2b216df06","tid":118086,"uid":52585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:32:47.000Z","msg":"6隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}